<eesti>Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri pidamise kord </eesti>
<inglise>Procedure for Maintenance of Estonian Central Register of Securities </inglise>
<eesti>Rahandusministri 28. detsembri 2000. a m&auml;&auml;rus nr 116 </eesti>
<inglise>Regulation No. 116 of the Minister of Finance of 28 December 2000 </inglise>
<eesti>(RTL 2000, 139, 2210), </eesti>
<inglise>(RTL (1) 2000, 139, 2210), </inglise>
<eesti>j&otilde;ustunud 1. jaanuaril 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>entered into force 1 January 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;&auml;rus kehtestatakse "Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri seaduse" (RT I 2000, 57, 373) paragrahvi 3 l&otilde;ike 2 ning paragrahvi 8 l&otilde;ike 1 alusel ja koosk&otilde;las paragrahvi 6 l&otilde;ikega 1, paragrahvi 12 l&otilde;igetega 1 ja 2, paragrahvi 15 l&otilde;igetega 1 ja 2, paragrahvi 19 l&otilde;ikega 1, paragrahvi 20 l&otilde;igetega 2 ja 6, paragrahvi 30 l&otilde;ikega 3, paragrahvi 31 l&otilde;ikega 2, paragrahvi 32 l&otilde;ikega 3, paragrahvi 35 l&otilde;ikega 3, paragrahvi 36 l&otilde;ikega 6, paragrahvi 37 l&otilde;ikega 5 ning paragrahvi 42 l&otilde;ikega 4. </eesti>
<inglise>This Regulation is established on the basis of subsections 3 (2) and 8 (1) and in accordance with subsections 6 (1), 12 (1) and (2), 15 (1) and (2), 19 (1), 20 (2) and (6), 30 (3), 31 (2), 32 (3), 35 (3), 36 (6), 37 (5) and 42 (4) of the Estonian Central Register of Securities Act (RT (2) I 2000, 57, 373). </inglise>
<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Reguleerimisala </eesti>
<inglise>Scope of application </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolev Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri pidamise kord (edaspidi kord) m&auml;&auml;rab kindlaks Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri (edaspidi register) pidamise korra, registrisse t&auml;iendavalt kantavate andmete loetelu, registrisse kannete tegemise korra, t&auml;iendavad n&otilde;uded kontohaldurile ning esindajakonto omanikule, samuti n&otilde;uded v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikele suunatud teatistele. </eesti>
<inglise>This Procedure for the Maintenance of the Estonian Central Register of Securities (hereinafter Procedure) establishes the procedure for the maintenance of the Estonian Central Register of Securities (hereinafter Register), the list of additional information to be entered in the register, the procedure for making register entries, additional requirements for account administrators and owners of nominee accounts, and the requirements regarding notices to owners of securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Registriandmete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Processing of register information </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registriandmete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine toimub automatiseeritud andmet&ouml;&ouml;tluse teel vastavalt registripidaja poolt kehtestatud andmet&ouml;&ouml;tluse reeglitele (edaspidi andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglid). </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Register information shall be processed by means of automatic data processing according to the rules for data processing established by the registrar (hereinafter data processing rules). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Muudatustest andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglites, samuti registriandmete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise tehniliste vahenditega seotud &uuml;mberkorraldustest, mis m&otilde;jutavad kontohaldurite tegevust, informeerib registripidaja kontohaldureid hiljemalt kaks kuud enne vastava muudatuse j&otilde;ustumist v&otilde;i tehnilise &uuml;mberkorralduse tegemist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall notify account administrators of any amendments to the data processing rules and of any restructuring relating to the technical means by which register information is processed, if such restructuring affects the activities of account administrators, at least two months before the entry into force of the relevant amendment or before the technical restructuring is carried out. </inglise>
<eesti>Eelnimetatud etteteatamist&auml;htaeg v&otilde;ib olla l&uuml;hem, kui selle kohta on andnud oma n&otilde;usoleku v&auml;hemalt 2/3 kontohalduritena tegutsevatest isikutest. </eesti>
<inglise>The term for giving the advance notice specified above may be shorter if at least two-thirds of the persons acting as account administrators have consented thereto. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Registriandmete s&auml;ilitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Preservation of register information </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja korraldab registriandmete s&auml;ilitamise viisil, mis tagab registriandmete kestvalt muutumatu s&auml;ilimise ning taasesitamise &otilde;igustatud isikutele ja ametiasutustele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall organise the preservation of register information in a manner which ensures preservation of the information in a permanently unaltered state and which enables reproduction thereof at the request of entitled persons and administrative agencies. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kande tegemiseks registripidajale esitatud andmeid ja dokumente s&auml;ilitab registripidaja "Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri seaduse" (edaspidi seadus) paragrahvi 30 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud tingimustel ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The information and documents submitted to the registrar in order for a register entry to be made shall be preserved by the registrar under the conditions and pursuant to the procedure provided for in subsection 30 (2) of the Estonian Central Register of Securities Act (hereinafter Act). </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse kantavad andmed </eesti>
<inglise>Information Subject to Entry in Register </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta </eesti>
<inglise>Information concerning securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimisel kantakse registrisse: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following information shall be entered in the Register upon registration of securities: </inglise>
<eesti>1) emitendi nimi, asukoht ja v&otilde;imaluse korral registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name, seat and, if possible, registry code of the issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite liik, nimiv&auml;&auml;rtus (koos v&auml;&auml;ringuga) ja kogus; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the type, nominal value (including currency) and amount of the securities; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omanike nimed, aadressid ja isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodid, isikukoodi puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the names, addresses, and personal identification codes or registry codes of the owners of the securities and, in the absence of a personal identification code, the date of birth; </inglise>
<eesti>4) andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite pantimise kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning pledges of securities; </inglise>
<eesti>5) registripidaja poolt omistatud rahvusvaheline v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite identifitseerimisnumber (ehk ISIN kood, edaspidi registrikood), mis eristab k&otilde;iki vastava emitendi samaliigilisi ja samav&auml;&auml;rsete &otilde;igustega v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid teistest registris registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest. </eesti>
<inglise>5) the International Securities Identification Number (or ISIN code, hereinafter registry code) allocated by the registrar, which distinguishes all of the relevant issuer's securities of the same type and representing equal rights from other securities entered in the Register. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja kannab v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta registrisse vastavasisulise m&auml;rke kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall make a notation concerning securities in the Register if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) emitendi p&otilde;hikirja v&otilde;i emissioonitingimustega on v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi v&otilde;&otilde;randamine piiratud kolmandate isikute suhtes kehtiva ostuees&otilde;igusega; </eesti>
<inglise>1) according to the issuer's articles of association or issue conditions, transfer of the title to securities is restricted by a right of pre-emption applying to third parties; </inglise>
<eesti>2) emitendi p&otilde;hikirja v&otilde;i emissioonitingimustega on piiratud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi koormamine pandiga; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the issuer's articles of association or issue conditions prescribe restrictions on encumbering the securities with a pledge; </inglise>
<eesti>3) osa v&otilde;&otilde;randamisel teisele osanikule on n&otilde;utav teiste osanike n&otilde;usolek. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the consent of other shareholders is required for the transfer of the title to a share in a private limited company to another shareholder. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto kohta </eesti>
<inglise>Information concerning securities accounts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto kohta kantakse registrisse j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following information shall be entered in the Register with regard to a securities account: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the address of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>3) f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku isikukood, selle puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) if the owner of the securities account is a natural person, his or her personal identification code or, in the absence thereof, date of birth; </inglise>
<eesti>4) juriidilisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku puhul viide registrile, kus juriidiline isik on registreeritud, ja registrikood, kui juriidiline isik on registreeritud; </eesti>
<inglise>4) if the owner of the securities account is a legal person, a reference to the register in which the legal person is registered, and the registry code if the legal person is registered; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku pangakonto number registriga seotud arveldusi teostavas krediidiasutuses ja selle krediidiasutuse &auml;rinimi; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the number of the bank account held by the owner of the securities account in a credit institution which performs transactions relating to the Register, and the business name of the credit institution; </inglise>
<eesti>6) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto number ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the number of the securities account and the date on which the securities account was opened; </inglise>
<eesti>7) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol olevate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kogus ja t&auml;histus; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the amount and denotation of the type of the securities in the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>8) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi mitmele isikule kuulumise korral v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi &uuml;histe omanike nimed, aadressid, isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodid (isikukoodi puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg) ning kaasomandi korral iga kaasomaniku proportsionaalne osa v&auml;&auml;rtpaberist v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest; </eesti>
<inglise>8) if a security is owned by several persons, the names, addresses and personal identification codes or registry codes (or, in the absence of a personal identification code, the date of birth) of the owners and, in the case of common ownership, the proportional share of each co-owner in the security or securities; </inglise>
<eesti>9) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omandamise aeg ja muude kannete tegemise ajad; </eesti>
<inglise>9) the time of acquisition of the securities and the times at which other entries are made; </inglise>
<eesti>10) muud seadusega s&auml;testatud andmed; </eesti>
<inglise>10) other information provided by law; </inglise>
<eesti>11) taotleja residentriik, mis avaldatakse tagamaks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberil p&otilde;hineva v&auml;ljamakse tegijale tulumaksu kinnipidamiseks vajaliku informatsiooni k&auml;ttesaadavus registri kaudu; </eesti>
<inglise>11) the country of residence of the applicant, which is disclosed in order to provide the person making payments on the basis of the security with access via the Register to the information necessary for withholding income tax; </inglise>
<eesti>12) taotleja n&otilde;usolekul andmed tema sidevahendite (telefoni ja/v&otilde;i telefaksi number ning v&otilde;imalusel elektronposti aadress) kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>12) with the consent of the applicant, information concerning the means of communication of the applicant (telephone and/or fax number, and, if possible, e-mail address); </inglise>
<eesti>13) andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte ning teiste v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikule suunatud teatiste edastamise tingimuste kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>13) information concerning the conditions for forwarding statements of the securities account and other notices to the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>14) &uuml;hise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto korral informatsioon selle kohta, kes on &otilde;igustatud k&auml;sutama &uuml;hisesse omandisse kuuluvaid v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid. </eesti>
<inglise>14) in the event of a joint securities account, information indicating the persons entitled to dispose of the securities in joint ownership. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) L&otilde;ike 1 punktides 11-14 loetletud andmed kantakse registrisse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontot omada sooviva isiku poolt kontohaldurile esitatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise taotluses n&auml;idatud andmete alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The information listed in clauses (1) 11) -14) shall be entered in the Register on the basis of the information provided in the application to open a securities account submitted to the account administrator by the person who wishes to own a securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Uuml;hise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto korral kantakse l&otilde;ike 1 punktis 11 nimetatud andmed registrisse nii isiku kohta, kelle nimel &uuml;hine v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avati, kui ka iga &uuml;hise omaniku kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the event of a joint securities account, the information entered in the Register according to clause (1) 11) shall include information concerning the person in whose name the joint securities account is opened and concerning each joint owner. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui &otilde;igusaktide kohaselt on olulise osaluse omandamiseks n&otilde;utav luba (edaspidi olulise osaluse omandamise luba), kannab registripidaja selleks p&auml;deva j&auml;relevalve teostaja taotluses n&auml;idatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto juurde olulise osaluse omandamise loa numbri, selle v&auml;ljaandmise kuup&auml;eva, vastava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikoodi ja osaluse suuruse, mille suhtes luba anti. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If, according to legislation, authorisation is required for the acquisition of a qualifying holding (hereinafter authorisation for the acquisition of a qualifying holding), the registrar shall enter the number of the authorisation for the acquisition of the qualifying holding, the date of issue of the authorisation, the registry code of the corresponding security and the size of the holding concerning which the authorisation applies in the Register with regard to the securities account indicated in the application from the competent supervisory authority. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid, mille suhtes olulise osaluse omandamise luba v&auml;lja anti, on registreeritud esindajakontol, kantakse eelmises l&otilde;ikes nimetatud andmed p&auml;deva j&auml;relevalve teostaja taotluses n&auml;idatud esindajakonto juurde koos olulise osaluse omandamise loa saanud isiku nime, isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodi ning aadressiga. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) If the securities with regard to which an authorisation for the acquisition of a qualifying holding is issued are registered on a nominee account, the information specified in the previous subsection shall be entered in the Register with regard to the nominee account indicated in the application from the competent supervisory authority together with the name, personal identification code or registry code, and address of the person to whom the authorisation for the acquisition of the qualifying holding is issued. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik teavitab kontohaldurit viivitamatult igast muudatusest tema poolt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamisel avaldatud andmetes. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) An owner of a securities account shall notify the account administrator promptly of any changes in the information submitted by the owner upon opening the securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande kohta </eesti>
<inglise>Information concerning transfer of securities </inglise>
<eesti>Lisaks seaduse s&auml;testatud andmetele kantakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande kohta registrisse m&auml;rge, kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande objektiks olnud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid omandati v&otilde;i v&otilde;&otilde;randati tasuta. </eesti>
<inglise>In addition to the information provided by the Act, a notation shall be made in the Register concerning a transfer of securities if the securities which were the object of the transfer were acquired or the title thereto was transferred without charge. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemise kord </eesti>
<inglise>Procedure for Making Register Entries </inglise>
<eesti>1. jagu </eesti>
<inglise>Division 1 </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemine emitendi taotlusel </eesti>
<inglise>Making of Entries at Request of Issuers </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Emitendi taotlusel tehtavad kanded </eesti>
<inglise>Entries made at request of issuers </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva korra paragrahvi 4 l&otilde;ike 1 punktides 1 ja 2 ning paragrahvi 4 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud andmete registreerimine ja muudatuste tegemine nimetatud andmetes toimub emitendi taotlusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Information specified in clauses 4 (1) 1) and 2) and subsection 4 (2) of this Procedure shall be registered and amendments shall be made to such information at the request of the issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse vormi, taotlusele lisatavate dokumentide ning andmete loetelu kehtestab registripidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>The format of the corresponding applications, and the list of documents and information to be annexed to the applications shall be established by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja teeb kanded taotluses s&auml;testatud tingimustel ja korras, kui &otilde;igusaktides pole s&auml;testatud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Unless otherwise provided by law, the registrar shall make entries under the conditions and pursuant to the procedure specified in the application. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui isikud, kelle v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodele tuleb kanded teha, m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks emitendi taotluses n&auml;idatud fikseerimisp&auml;eva alusel, v&otilde;etakse kannete tegemise aluseks registriandmed fikseerimisp&auml;eva alguse seisuga (kell 0.00), kui emitent pole taotluses m&auml;&auml;ranud teist kellaaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If the persons in whose securities accounts entries are to be made are determined on the basis of the fixed day specified in the application made by the issuer, the entries shall be made on the basis of the register information as at the beginning of the fixed day (at 0.00) unless the issuer has indicated a different time in the application. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja keeldub kannete tegemisest, kui taotlus ei vasta registripidaja kehtestatud v&otilde;i &otilde;igusaktides s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i kui taotluses n&otilde;utud kannete tegemine oleks vastuolus seadusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar shall refuse to make entries if the application is not in compliance with the requirements established by the registrar or provided by legislation or if making the entries requested in the application would be contrary to law. </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemisest keeldumisest ning selle p&otilde;hjustest tuleb taotluse esitajat viivitamatult teavitada. </eesti>
<inglise>The person submitting the application shall be notified promptly of refusal to make entries and of the reasons for such refusal. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite t&auml;iendava emissiooni registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of additional issue of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registris eelnevalt registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite t&auml;iendava emissiooni (edaspidi t&auml;iendavad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid) registreerib registripidaja hiljemalt viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates taotluse vastuv&otilde;tmisest, kui emitent pole taotluses m&auml;&auml;ranud kannete tegemiseks pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall register an additional issue of securities which have been previously entered in the Register (hereinafter additional securities) not later than within five working days as of the receipt of the corresponding application from the issuer unless the application sets out a longer term for making the entries. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui t&auml;iendavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omandamiseks &otilde;igustatud isikud m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks emitendi taotluses n&auml;idatud fikseerimisp&auml;eva alusel, teeb registripidaja t&auml;iendavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimiseks vajalikud kanded hiljemalt kahe t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates fikseerimisp&auml;eva saabumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the persons entitled to acquire additional securities are determined on the basis of the fixed day specified in the application made by the issuer, the registrar shall make the entries necessary for registration of the additional securities not later than within two working days as of the beginning of the fixed day. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) T&auml;iendavate aktsiate ja osade registreerimisel teeb registripidaja vastavalt t&auml;iendavatele aktsiatele v&otilde;i osadele m&auml;rke (edaspidi ajutine registrikood). </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon registration of additional shares, the registrar shall make a notation (hereinafter temporary registry code) on the additional shares. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ajutise registrikoodiga aktsiatele v&otilde;i osadele annab registripidaja eelnevalt registreeritud aktsiate v&otilde;i osade registrikoodi, kui aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamise kanne on tehtud &auml;riregistrisse ning kui t&auml;iendavatest aktsiatest v&otilde;i osadest tulenevad &otilde;igused ei erine eelnevalt registreeritud aktsiatest v&otilde;i osadest tulenevatest &otilde;igustest. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar shall allocate the registry code of previously registered shares to shares with a temporary registry code if an entry concerning an increase in share capital has been made in the commercial register and if the rights arising from the additional shares do not differ from the rights arising from the previously registered shares. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Alteration of nominal value of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja teeb v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmiseks vajalikud kanded hiljemalt 2 t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates taotluse vastuv&otilde;tmisest, kui emitent pole taotluses m&auml;&auml;ranud kannete tegemiseks pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall make entries necessary for altering the nominal value of securities not later than within two working days as of the receipt of the corresponding application from the issuer unless the application sets out a longer term for making the entries. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui isikud, kelle v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmine puudutab, m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks emitendi taotluses n&auml;idatud fikseerimisp&auml;eva alusel, teeb registripidaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmiseks vajalikud kanded hiljemalt kahe t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates fikseerimisp&auml;eva saabumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the persons whose securities are subject to an alteration in nominal value are determined on the basis of the fixed day specified in the application made by the issuer, the registrar shall make the entries necessary for the alteration of the nominal value of the securities not later than within two working days as of the beginning of the fixed day. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Osa nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse suurendamisel seoses osakapitali suurendamisega annab registripidaja osa nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse suurendamise arvel saadud osale ajutise registrikoodi. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If the nominal value of a share in a private limited company is increased due to an increase in share capital, the registrar shall allocate a temporary registry code to the shares acquired as a result of the increase in the nominal value of the share. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajutise registrikoodiga t&auml;histatud osadele annab registripidaja eelnevalt registreeritud osade registrikoodi, kui osakapitali suurendamise kanne on tehtud &auml;riregistrisse ning kui osa suurendamise arvel saadud osadest tulenevad &otilde;igused ei erine eelnevalt registreeritud osadest tulenevatest &otilde;igustest. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall allocate the registry code of previously registered shares to shares with a temporary registry code if an entry concerning an increase in share capital has been made in the commercial register and if the rights arising from the shares acquired as a result of the increase in the nominal value of the shares do not differ from the rights arising from the previously registered shares. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Osade nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamisel seoses osakapitali v&auml;hendamisega annab registripidaja osa nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamise suurust v&auml;ljendavatele osadele ajutise registrikoodi. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the nominal value of a share in a private limited company is reduced due to a reduction of share capital, the registrar shall allocate a temporary registry code to the shares which indicate the extent of the reduction in the nominal value of the share. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajutise registrikoodiga t&auml;histatud osad kustutab registripidaja registrist p&auml;rast seda, kui osakapitali v&auml;hendamise kanne on tehtud &auml;riregistrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall delete shares with a temporary registry code from the Register after the entry concerning the reduction of share capital is made in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Aktsiate nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmiseks vajalikud kanded teeb registripidaja esimesel v&otilde;imalusel p&auml;rast seda, kui aktsia nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmise otsuse j&otilde;ustumiseks vajalik kanne on tehtud &auml;riregistrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Entries necessary for altering the nominal value of a share in a public limited company shall be made by the Registrar at the earliest opportunity after the entry necessary for the entry into force of the decision concerning alteration of the nominal value of the share is made in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite vahetamine </eesti>
<inglise>Exchange of securities </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja teeb v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite vahetamiseks vajalikud kanded hiljemalt viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates taotluse vastuv&otilde;tmisest, kui emitent pole taotluses m&auml;&auml;ranud kannete tegemiseks pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall make entries necessary for the exchange of securities not later than within five working days as of the receipt of the corresponding application from the issuer unless the application sets out a longer term for making the entries. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamine </eesti>
<inglise>Deletion of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja teeb v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamise kanded hiljemalt kahe t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates taotluse vastuv&otilde;tmisest, kui emitent pole taotluses m&auml;&auml;ranud kannete tegemiseks pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall make entries for the deletion of securities not later than within two working days as of the receipt of the corresponding application from the issuer unless the application sets out a longer term for making the entries. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui isikud, kelle v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid kuuluvad kustutamisele, m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks emitendi taotluses n&auml;idatud fikseerimisp&auml;eva alusel, teeb registripidaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamise kanded hiljemalt kahe t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates fikseerimisp&auml;eva saabumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the persons whose securities are subject to deletion are determined on the basis of the fixed day specified in the application made by the issuer, the registrar shall make the entries necessary for the deletion of the securities not later than within two working days as of the beginning of the fixed day. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Aktsiate ja osade kustutamisel seoses aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamisega, annab registripidaja vastavalt kustutamisele kuuluvatele aktsiatele v&otilde;i osadele ajutise registrikoodi. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If shares are deleted due to a reduction of share capital, the registrar shall allocate a temporary registry code to the shares subject to deletion. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajutise registrikoodiga t&auml;histatud aktsiad v&otilde;i osad kustutab registripidaja p&auml;rast seda, kui aktsia v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamise kanne on tehtud &auml;riregistrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall delete shares with a temporary registry code after the entry concerning the reduction of share capital is made in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>2. jagu </eesti>
<inglise>Division 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemine kontohalduri, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi korraldaja ja kontos&uuml;steemi pidaja korraldusel </eesti>
<inglise>Making of Entries Ordered by Account Administrators, Stock Exchange Operators and Operators of Account Handling Systems </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Kande tegemine kontohalduri korraldusel </eesti>
<inglise>Making of entries ordered by account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduri poolt registripidajale korralduse andmine, kande tegemise ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi blokeerimise ajaline re&zcaron;iim ning kandega seotud rahalised arveldused toimuvad vastavalt seaduses, k&auml;esolevas korras ja andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglites s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The issue of orders to the registrar by account administrators, determination of the time limits for making entries and freezing securities, and cash settlements relating to entries shall be effected pursuant to the provisions of the Act, this Procedure and data processing rules. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohaldur on kohustatud registritoimingu tegemiseks talle antud korralduse registripidajale andma viivitamatult p&auml;rast korralduse saamist selleks &otilde;igustatud isikult, kui viimane pole korralduse registripidajale edastamiseks antud k&auml;sundis ette n&auml;inud teistsugust t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An account administrator is required to communicate an order issued thereto for the making of a registry entry to the registrar promptly after receipt of the order from the entitled person unless the latter has specified a different term in the agreement authorising the account administrator to communicate the order to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui k&otilde;ik kande tegemiseks vajalikud, &otilde;igusaktides ja andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeeglites s&auml;testatud eeldused ja n&otilde;uded on t&auml;idetud, teeb registripidaja kande kontohalduri poolt antud korralduse alusel esimesel andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglites s&auml;testatud v&otilde;imalusel, kui korralduses endas ei ole m&auml;&auml;ratud kande tegemiseks hilisemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If all the requirements which are necessary for an entry to be made and which are provided in legislation and the data processing rules are complied with, the registrar shall make an entry on the basis of the order given by an account administrator at the earliest opportunity provided in the data processing rules unless the order sets out a longer term for making the entry. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui kontohalduri korralduse kohaselt on v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande tegemise tingimuseks rahaliste kohustuste eelnev arveldamine, teeb registripidaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande juhul, kui on toimunud &uuml;lekandekorralduse andnud kontohaldurite vaheliste rahaliste n&otilde;uete ja kohustuste arveldamine. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the order of an account administrator prescribes prior settlement of financial obligations as a precondition for a transfer of securities, the registrar shall transfer the securities after the settlement of financial claims and obligations between the account administrators who issued the transfer order. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lekande objektiks olevad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid blokeerib registripidaja enne v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande tegemist debiteeritaval v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol. </eesti>
<inglise>Before transferring the securities, the registrar shall freeze the securities which are the object of the transfer in the securities account to be debited. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Korraldamaks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekannete tegemisega seotud rahalisi arveldusi, s&otilde;lmib registripidaja lepingu Eesti Panga ja/v&otilde;i isikuga, kellel on &otilde;igusaktide kohaselt &otilde;igus teha rahaliste arvelduste korraldamiseks vajalikke tehinguid ja toiminguid. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) In order to organise cash settlements relating to transfers of securities, the registrar shall enter into an agreement with the Bank of Estonia and/or a person who, pursuant to legislation, has the right to perform transactions and acts necessary for organising cash settlements. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Kande tegemine v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi korraldaja ja kontos&uuml;steemi pidaja korraldusel </eesti>
<inglise>Making of entries ordered by stock exchange operators or operators of account handling systems </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Lisaks seaduse paragrahvi 12 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud alustele v&otilde;ib kande aluseks olla "V&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru seaduse" (RT I 1993, 35, 543; 1995, 22, 328; 1996, 26, 528; 1997, 34, 535; 1998, 61, 979; 2000, 10, 55) paragrahvi 2 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis 1 nimetatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi (edaspidi v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi korraldaja) ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&otilde;i sarnaste finantsinstrumentide registri, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiarvelduss&uuml;steemi haldaja v&otilde;i keskdepositooriumi pidaja (edaspidi kontos&uuml;steemi pidaja) korraldus. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In addition to the bases provided for in subsection 12 (1) of the Act, an entry may be made also on the basis of the order of a stock exchange specified in clause 2 (1) 1) of the Securities Market Act (RT I 1993, 35, 543; 1995, 22, 328; 1996, 26, 528; 1997, 34, 535; 1998, 61, 979; 2000, 10, 55) (hereinafter stock exchange operator), a register of securities or other similar financial instruments, an administrator of a securities settlement system, or the registrar of the central depository (hereinafter operator of an account handling system). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi korraldaja poolt korralduste registripidajale andmise viis, n&otilde;uded korraldustes sisalduva informatsiooni sisule, kande tegemise tingimused ja kord ning vajadusel ka kannetega seotud rahaliste arvelduste kord n&auml;hakse ette registripidaja ja vastava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsi korraldaja vahelises lepingus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The method of communicating the orders of a stock exchange operator to the registrar, requirements regarding the content of such orders, the conditions of and procedure for making the entries and, if necessary, the procedure for performing cash settlements relating to the entries shall be prescribed in an agreement entered into by the registrar and the stock exchange operator. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kontos&uuml;steemi pidaja korralduste registripidajale andmise viis, n&otilde;uded korraldustes sisalduva informatsiooni sisule, kande tegemise tingimused ja kord, sealhulgas kontos&uuml;steemis registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite &uuml;lekandmine v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kontos&uuml;steemist registrisse ja/v&otilde;i registrist v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kontos&uuml;steemi ning vajadusel ka kandega seotud rahaliste arvelduste kord n&auml;hakse ette registripidaja ja vastava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kontos&uuml;steemi pidaja vahelises lepingus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The method of communicating the orders of the operator of a securities account handling system to the registrar, requirements regarding the content of such orders, the conditions of and procedure for making the entries, including transfer of securities registered in the securities account handling system from the securities account handling system to the register and/or from the register to the securities account handling system and, if necessary, the procedure for performing cash settlements relating to the entries shall be prescribed in an agreement entered into by the registrar and the operator of the securities account handling system. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur </eesti>
<inglise>Account Administrator </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse taotlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Application for status of account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduri staatuse taotlemiseks esitatakse registripidajale j&auml;rgmised dokumendid: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to apply for the status of an account administrator, the following documents shall be submitted to the registrar: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kirjalik taotlus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a written application; </inglise>
<eesti>2) taotleja p&otilde;hikiri; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the articles of association of the applicant; </inglise>
<eesti>3) taotluse esitaja volitusi t&otilde;endav registri v&auml;ljav&otilde;te; </eesti>
<inglise>3) an extract from a register, certifying the authority of the person submitting the application; </inglise>
<eesti>4) t&otilde;estatud koopia v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusloast; </eesti>
<inglise>4) a certified copy of the activity licence of the professional securities market participant; </inglise>
<eesti>5) aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurust t&otilde;endav registri v&auml;ljav&otilde;te; </eesti>
<inglise>5) an extract from a register, certifying the amount of share capital; </inglise>
<eesti>6) selgitav &uuml;levaade sellest, kuidas tagatakse &otilde;igusaktidest ja andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglitest tulenevate kohustuste ja n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmine ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekannetega seotud rahaliste arvelduste korraldamine. </eesti>
<inglise>6) an overview describing the measures to ensure compliance with obligations and requirements arising from legislation and the data processing rules and to ensure the organisation of cash settlements relating to securities and transfers of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Euroopa Liidu liikmesriigis registreeritud &auml;ri&uuml;hing, millele on antud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusluba, samuti &auml;ri&uuml;hing, mis on registreeritud riigis, mis ei ole Euroopa Liidu liikmesriik, kuid millega Eesti Vabariigil on j&otilde;ustunud vastastikuse &otilde;igusabi osutamise leping, ning millele on antud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusluba, lisab eelmise l&otilde;ike punktis 1 nimetatud taotlusele tema asukohariigi p&auml;deva j&auml;relevalve teostaja kinnituse selle kohta, et taotlejale asukohariigi &otilde;iguse kohaselt antud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusluba annab &otilde;iguse tegutseda kontohaldurina. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Companies which hold an activity licence of a professional securities market participant and are registered in a Member State of the European Union, and companies which hold an activity licence of a professional securities market participant and are registered in a country which is not a Member State of the European Union but with which the Republic of Estonia has an agreement of mutual legal assistance which has entered into force shall annex to the application specified in clause 1) of the previous section confirmation from a competent supervisory authority of their home country certifying that, according to the activity licence of a professional securities market participant granted to the applicant pursuant to the legislation of the home country, the applicant has the right to operate as an account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja v&otilde;ib n&otilde;uda lisaks eelloetletud dokumentidele t&auml;iendavaid andmeid v&otilde;i dokumente, samuti teostada kokkuleppel taotlejaga viimase juures kohapealset kontrolli, kui see on vajalik veendumaks kontohalduri kohustuste t&auml;itmiseks vajalike eelduste olemasolus v&otilde;i esitatud dokumentide v&otilde;i neis sisalduvate andmete &otilde;igsuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In addition to the documents listed above, the registrar may require submission of additional information or documents and, by agreement with the applicant, conduct on-site inspections of the applicant if this necessary to prove that the applicant is in a position to perform the obligations of an account administrator or that the documents submitted are authentic or the information contained therein is correct. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Otsuse kontohalduri staatuse andmise v&otilde;i sellest keeldumise kohta teeb registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu hiljemalt 20 t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates l&otilde;igetes 1-3 nimetatud teabe ja dokumentide laekumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The supervisory board of the registrar shall make a decision concerning the grant of or refusal to grant the status of an account administrator not later than within twenty working days as of receipt of the information and documents specified in subsections (1) -(3). </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu keeldub kontohalduri staatuse andmisest, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The supervisory board of the registrar shall refuse to grant the status of an account administrator if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu hinnangul ei ole t&auml;idetud k&otilde;ik eeldused &otilde;igusaktidest ning andmet&ouml;&ouml;tlusreeglitest tulenevate kohustuste ja n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekannetega seotud rahaliste arvelduste korraldamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>1) in the opinion of the supervisory board of the registrar, the applicant is not in a position to meet all the obligations and requirements arising from legislation and the data processing rules or to perform cash settlements relating to securities and transfers of securities; </inglise>
<eesti>2) taotleja aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapital ei ole ekvivalentne v&auml;hemalt 125 000 euroga vastavalt Eesti Panga kursile. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the share capital of the applicant is not equivalent to at least 125 000 euro on the basis of the exchange rate of the Bank of Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kontohalduri staatuse andmise otsus v&otilde;i kontohalduri staatuse andmisest keeldumise motiveeritud otsus saadetakse viivitamatult taotlejale. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A decision to grant the status of an account administrator or a reasoned decision to refuse to grant the status of an account administrator shall be sent to the applicant promptly. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuses tegutsemise leping </eesti>
<inglise>Agreement with person acting as account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduri staatuse omandanud isik ja registripidaja s&otilde;lmivad lepingu, kus n&auml;hakse muuhulgas ette kontohalduri staatuse omandanud isiku poolt vahendatavad teenused, tegevuse alustamise tingimused (kindlustus) ja kord ning muud seaduses s&auml;testatud tingimused. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A person who has acquired the status of an account administrator and the registrar shall enter into an agreement which prescribes, inter alia, the services offered by the person with the status of an account administrator, the conditions (insurance) and the procedure for commencing activities, and other conditions provided for in the Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatuse omandanud isik peab alustama oma tegevust kontohaldurina l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud lepingus etten&auml;htud t&auml;htaja jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A person who has acquired the status of an account administrator shall commence activities as an account administrator within the term prescribed in the agreement specified in subsection (1). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse peatamine </eesti>
<inglise>Suspension of status as account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus peatada kontohalduri staatus seaduse paragrahvi 35 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar has the right to suspend a person's status as an account administrator on the bases provided for in subsection 35 (1) of the Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatuse peatamine seisneb piirangute seadmises kontohalduri korralduste ja/v&otilde;i p&auml;ringute vastuv&otilde;tmisele ja/v&otilde;i t&auml;itmisele registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu otsuse alusel otsuses n&auml;idatud ulatuses kas osaliselt (edaspidi osaline peatamine) v&otilde;i t&auml;ielikult (edaspidi t&auml;ielik peatamine). </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Suspension of a person's status as an account administrator means the imposition of restrictions on the receipt and/or execution of orders and/or inquiries made by the account administrator on the basis of and to the extent specified in a decision of the supervisory board of the registrar either partially (hereinafter partial suspension) or totally (hereinafter total suspension). </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduri staatuse peatamise otsustab registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Suspension of a person's status as an account administrator shall be decided by the supervisory board of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Olles saanud p&otilde;hjendatud taotluse kontohalduri staatuse peatamise kohta, kutsub n&otilde;ukogu esimees v&otilde;i teda asendav n&otilde;ukogu liige kokku registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu koosoleku, millel otsustatakse kontohalduri staatuse peatamise &uuml;le. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) After receipt of a reasoned request for the suspension of a person's status as an account administrator, the chairman of the supervisory board or the board member substituting for the chairman shall call a meeting of the supervisory board of the registrar at which a decision shall be taken on the suspension of the person's status as an account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Otsuses kontohalduri staatuse peatamise kohta tuleb n&auml;idata: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A decision concerning suspension of a person's status as an account administrator shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontohalduri staatuse peatamise p&otilde;hjendus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the reason for the suspension of the person's status as an account administrator; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kontohalduri staatuse peatamise ulatus (t&auml;ielik v&otilde;i osaline); </eesti>
<inglise>2) the extent of the suspension of the person's status as an account administrator (total or partial); </inglise>
<eesti>3) osalise peatamise korral piirangute kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) in the case of partial suspension, a description of the restrictions; </inglise>
<eesti>4) t&auml;htaeg kontohalduri staatuse peatamist tinginud asjaolude k&otilde;rvaldamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>4) a term for elimination of the circumstances which caused the suspension of the person's status as an account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kontohalduri staatuse peatamise otsus saadetakse viivitamatult kontohaldurile, kelle staatus peatati, samuti teistele tegutsevatele kontohalduritele. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A decision concerning suspension of a person's status as an account administrator shall be sent promptly to the account administrator whose status is suspended and to other operating account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Kontohalduri staatuse peatamisest teavitatakse avalikkust &uuml;ldsusele avatud arvutis&uuml;steemi kaudu. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The suspension of a person's status as an account administrator shall be made public through a computer system available to the public. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamine </eesti>
<inglise>Revocation of status as account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja t&uuml;histab kontohalduri staatuse seaduse paragrahvi 36 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall revoke a person's status as an account administrator on the bases provided for in subsection 36 (1) of the Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise otsustab registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Revocation of a person's status as an account administrator shall be decided by the supervisory board of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Olles saanud p&otilde;hjendatud taotluse kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise kohta, kutsub n&otilde;ukogu esimees v&otilde;i teda asendav n&otilde;ukogu liige kokku registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu koosoleku, millel otsustatakse kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise &uuml;le. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) After receipt of a reasoned request for the revocation of a person's status as an account administrator, the chairman of the supervisory board or the board member substituting for the chairman shall call a meeting of the supervisory board of the registrar at which a decision shall be taken on the revocation of the person's status as an account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Otsuses kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise kohta tuleb n&auml;idata: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A decision concerning revocation of a person's status as an account administrator shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise p&otilde;hjendus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the reason for the revocation of the person's status as an account administrator; </inglise>
<eesti>2) seaduse paragrahvi 36 l&otilde;ike 3 punktides 1 ja 2 s&auml;testatud andmed ning muud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode haldamis&otilde;iguse &uuml;leandmisega seotud tingimused ja asjaolud. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the information provided for in clauses 36 (3) 1) and 2) of the Act and other conditions and circumstances relating to transfer of the right to administer securities accounts; </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise otsus saadetakse viivitamatult isikule, kelle kontohalduri staatus t&uuml;histati, samuti teistele tegutsevatele kontohalduritele. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A decision concerning revocation of a person's status as an account administrator shall be sent promptly to the person whose status as an account administrator is revoked and to other operating account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamisest teavitatakse avalikkust seaduse paragrahvi 36 l&otilde;ikes 5 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The revocation of a person's status as an account administrator shall be made public pursuant to the procedure provided for in subsection 36 (5) of the Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse kaotanud v&otilde;i sellest loobunud isiku kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Obligations of persons who have lost or renounced status of account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Isik, kelle kontohalduri staatus on t&uuml;histatud, samuti isik, kes on kontohalduri staatusest loobunud, on kohustatud t&auml;itma registripidaja korraldusi ja n&otilde;udeid, mille eesm&auml;rgiks on tagada v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanike huvide kaitse ning teiste kontohaldurite h&auml;irimatu tegevus. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A person whose status as an account administrator has been revoked or who has renounced such status is required to comply with the orders and requirements of the registrar aimed at ensuring that the interests of the owners of securities accounts are protected and that the activities of other account administrators continue undisturbed. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) L&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud isik korraldab k&otilde;igi temale registritoimingute ja p&auml;ringute tegemiseks antud korralduste aluseks olevate andmete ja dokumentide arhiveerimise viisil, mis tagab eelnimetatud andmete ja dokumentide s&auml;ilimise ning k&auml;ttesaadavuse &otilde;igustatud isikutele ja ametiasutustele v&auml;hemalt k&uuml;mne aasta jooksul, arvates kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise otsuse tegemisest v&otilde;i registripidaja ja kontohaldurina tegutsenud isiku vahelise lepingu l&otilde;ppemisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Archival processing of all information and documents which were the basis for the orders issued to a person specified in subsection (1) for making register entries or inquiries shall be organised by the person in a manner which ensures that the aforementioned information and documents are preserved and that entitled persons and government agencies have access thereto for at least ten years as of the decision on revocation of the person's status as an account administrator being made or the contract between the registrar and the person operating as an account administrator being terminated. </inglise>
<eesti>5. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 5 </inglise>
<eesti>N&otilde;uded esindajakonto omanikule </eesti>
<inglise>Requirements for Owners of Nominee Accounts </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 19. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 19. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto avamise ja omamise tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Conditions for opening and ownership of nominee accounts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohaldur edastab registripidajale esindajakonto avamise taotluse &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui esindajakontot omada sooviv isik vastab seaduses ja k&auml;esolevas korras s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An account administrator shall forward an application for opening a nominee account to the registrar only if the person who wishes to own a nominee account meets the requirements provided for in the Act and this Procedure. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Esindajakonto aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapital peab olema ekvivalentne v&auml;hemalt 730 000 euroga vastavalt Eesti Panga kursile. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The share capital of the owner of a nominee account shall be equivalent to at least 730 000 euro on the basis of the exchange rate of the Bank of Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Esindajakonto omanik on kohustatud &otilde;igusaktides s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetest k&otilde;rvalekaldumisest viivitamatult teavitama seaduse paragrahvi 38 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud j&auml;relevalve teostajat, registripidajat ja kontohaldurit. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The owner of a nominee account is required to notify the supervisory authority specified in subsection 38 (1) of the Act, the registrar and the account administrator promptly of any deviation from the requirements provided by legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 20. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 20. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmete avaldamine esindajakonto omaniku poolt </eesti>
<inglise>Submission of information by owner of nominee account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Esindajakonto omanik avaldab seaduse paragrahv 6 l&otilde;ikes 7 nimetatud andmed (edaspidi andmed) j&auml;relevalve teostajale, samuti registripidajale kirjaliku v&otilde;i kirjalikku taasesitamist ja isiku identifitseerimist v&otilde;imaldava n&otilde;ude alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The owner of a nominee account shall submit the information specified in subsection 6 (7) of the Act (hereinafter information) to the supervisory authority and, on the basis of a written request or a request enabling written reproduction and identification of the person, to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) L&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud n&otilde;udes tuleb n&auml;idata: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A request specified in subsection (1) shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood, mille kohta andmeid n&otilde;utakse; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code of the security concerning which information is requested; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kuup&auml;ev ja kellaaeg, millise seisuga andmeid n&otilde;utakse; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the date and time as at which the information is requested; </inglise>
<eesti>3) informatsioon selle kohta, kas andmeid n&otilde;utakse k&otilde;igi klientide, &uuml;ksnes kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud tunnustele vastavate klientide v&otilde;i konkreetse kliendi kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>3) information stating whether the information is requested concerning all clients, only clients corresponding to certain characteristics, or a specific client; </inglise>
<eesti>4) informatsioon n&otilde;utavate andmete ulatuse ja vormi kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning the extent and format of the requested information; </inglise>
<eesti>5) informatsioon andmete j&auml;relevalve teostajale v&otilde;i registripidajale edastamise viisi ja t&auml;htaja kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>5) information concerning the means of and term for communication of the information to the supervisory authority or the registrar; </inglise>
<eesti>6) muu asjakohane informatsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>6) other relevant information. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Esindajakonto omanik edastab andmed j&auml;relevalve teostajale v&otilde;i registripidajale n&otilde;udes n&auml;idatud tingimustel hiljemalt eelmise l&otilde;ike punktis 5 s&auml;testatud t&auml;htaja jooksul, mis ei v&otilde;i olla l&uuml;hem kui kolm t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The owner of a nominee account shall communicate the information to the supervisory authority or registrar under the conditions specified in the request and not later than within the term provided for in subsection (5) of the previous section, which shall not be shorter than three working days. </inglise>
<eesti>6. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 6 </inglise>
<eesti>Andmete avaldamine ja teatiste v&auml;ljastamine registripidaja poolt </eesti>
<inglise>Disclosure of Information and Issue of Notices by Registrar </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 21. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 21. </inglise>
<eesti>Registritoiminguid iseloomustavate andmete avaldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Disclosure of information concerning register entries </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Emitendi taotlusel tehtavate registritoimingute kohta avaldab registripidaja &uuml;ldsusele avatud arvutis&uuml;steemis teate, milles n&auml;idatakse registritoimingut taotlev emitent (emitendi nimi ja v&otilde;imalusel registrikood) ning muud k&auml;esolevas korras s&auml;testatud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A notice concerning registry entries made at the request of an issuer shall be published by the registrar through a computer system available to the public and the notice shall set out the issuer requesting the register entry (the name and, if possible, registry code of the issuer) and other information provided for in this Procedure. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimise, samuti t&auml;iendavalt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimise kohta avaldatavas teates n&auml;idatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A notice published concerning the registration of securities or additionally issued securities shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberile antud registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code allocated to the security; </inglise>
<eesti>2) t&auml;iendavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimisel ajutine registrikood, kui see antakse t&auml;iendavalt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitele; </eesti>
<inglise>2) in the case of registration of additional securities, the temporary registry code if such code is allocated to the additionally issued securities; </inglise>
<eesti>3) registreeritava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi liiki kajastav nimetus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the name indicating the type of security registered; </inglise>
<eesti>4) v&otilde;imalusel v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi nimiv&auml;&auml;rtus koos v&auml;&auml;ringuga; </eesti>
<inglise>4) if possible, the nominal value and currency of the security; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kogus; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the amount of securities; </inglise>
<eesti>6) v&otilde;imalusel kannete tegemise kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>6) if possible, the date on which the entries were made. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmise kohta avaldatavas teates n&auml;idatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A notice published concerning alteration of the nominal value of securities shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood ja nimetus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code and name of the security; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi endine ja uus nimiv&auml;&auml;rtus; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the former and new nominal value of the security; </inglise>
<eesti>3) ajutine registrikood, kui nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamise v&otilde;i suurendamise kohta kantakse registrisse ajutine registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the temporary registry code, if such code is entered in the Register concerning a reduction or increase in nominal value; </inglise>
<eesti>4) v&otilde;imalusel kannete tegemise kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>4) if possible, the date on which the entries were made. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite asendamise kohta avaldatavas teates n&auml;idatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A notice published concerning the conversion of securities shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) asendatava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code of the security to be converted; </inglise>
<eesti>2) asendava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood, kui asendav v&auml;&auml;rtpaber on registris registreeritud; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the registry code of the converted security if it is entered in the Register; </inglise>
<eesti>3) asendava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi emitendi nimi ja v&otilde;imalusel registrikood, kui asendava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi emitent ja asendatava v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi emitent on erinevad; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the name and, if possible, the registry code of the issuer of the converted security if the issuer of the converted security is not the issuer of the security to be converted; </inglise>
<eesti>4) asendussuhe; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the conversion rate; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&otilde;imalusel kannete tegemise kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>5) if possible, the date on which the entries were made. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamise kohta avaldatavas teates n&auml;idatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A notice published concerning the deletion of securities shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) registrist kustutamisele kuuluva v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood ja nimetus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code and name of the security subject to deletion from the Register; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kustutamisele kuuluvate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite arv; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the number of securities subject to deletion; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamise kohta kantakse registrisse ajutine registrikood - ajutine registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the temporary registry code if such code is entered in the Register concerning the deletion of the securities; </inglise>
<eesti>4) v&otilde;imalusel kannete tegemise kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>4) if possible, the date on which the entries were made. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Lisaks l&otilde;igetes 2-5 nimetatud andmetele v&otilde;ib registripidaja avaldada k&auml;esolevas korras nimetamata andmeid, kui need omavad t&auml;htsust seonduvalt registritoimingu t&auml;itmiseks tehtavate kannetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) In addition to the information specified in subsections (2) -(5), the registrar may publish information not specified in this Procedure if such information is relevant to the register entries to be made. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Lisaks k&auml;esolevas paragrahvis s&auml;testatud andmetele v&otilde;ib registripidaja avaldada informatsiooni, mis on seotud registris registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest tulenevate &otilde;igustega (dividendi maksmine jms). </eesti>
<inglise>(7) In addition to the information provided for in this section, the registrar may publish information relating to the rights arising from the securities entered in the Register (payment of dividends, etc.). </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Registripidaja avaldab registritoiminguga seotud andmeid sisaldava teate &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui registritoimingu t&auml;itmiseks vajalike kannete tegemiseks on t&auml;idetud k&otilde;ik &otilde;igusaktides etten&auml;htud ja registripidaja poolt kehtestatud n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The registrar shall publish a notice containing information relating to a register entry only if all the requirements prescribed by legislation and established by the registrar for the making of the register entry are met. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte edastamine emitendile </eesti>
<inglise>Communication of extracts concerning securities to issuer </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Seaduse paragrahvi 19 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte v&auml;ljastab registripidaja emitendi kirjaliku v&otilde;i kirjalikku taasesitamist ja isiku identifitseerimist v&otilde;imaldava n&otilde;ude alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall issue an extract specified in subsection 19 (1) of the Act on the basis of a written request from the issuer or a request enabling written reproduction and identification of the person. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) L&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud n&otilde;udes tuleb n&auml;idata: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A request specified in subsection (1) shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registrikood, mille kohta v&auml;ljav&otilde;tet soovitakse; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the registry code of the security concerning which the extract is requested; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kuup&auml;ev ja kellaaeg, millise seisuga v&auml;ljav&otilde;tet soovitakse; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the date and time as at which the extract is requested; </inglise>
<eesti>3) m&auml;rge v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte vormi kohta (kas v&auml;ljav&otilde;tet soovitakse paberkujul v&otilde;i elektroonsel andmekandjal); </eesti>
<inglise>3) a notation concerning the format of the extract (whether the extract is requested on paper or in electronic form); </inglise>
<eesti>4) informatsioon v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte edastamise v&otilde;i &uuml;leandmise tingimuste kohta l&auml;htuvalt l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatust; </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning the conditions of communication or delivery of the extract according to the provisions of subsection (3); </inglise>
<eesti>5) muud n&otilde;ude sisu t&auml;psustavad andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>5) other information specifying the content of the request. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&auml;ljav&otilde;te edastatakse emitendile turvalist andmevahetust v&otilde;imaldaval viisil arvutiv&otilde;rgu kaudu, antakse &uuml;le emitendi selleks volitatud esindajale allkirja vastu v&otilde;i edastatakse emitendile posti teel. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An extract concerning securities shall be communicated to the issuer through a computer network in a manner which ensures the secure exchange of data, delivered to the authorised representative of the issuer against a signature, or sent to the issuer by post. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja keeldub v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte edastamisest v&otilde;i &uuml;leandmisest, kui emitendi n&otilde;ue ei vasta k&auml;esolevas korras s&auml;testatud tingimustele v&otilde;i kui emitent keeldub registripidaja hinnakirjas s&auml;testatud tasu maksmisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar shall refuse to communicate or deliver an extract if the request of the issuer is not in compliance with the requirements provided for in this Procedure or if the issuer refuses to pay the fee provided for in the price list of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>Teatis v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kohta </eesti>
<inglise>Notice concerning opening of securities account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Seaduse paragrahvi 20 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud teatis v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kohta peab sisaldama allj&auml;rgnevaid andmeid: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A notice concerning the opening of a securities account as specified in subsection 20 (1) of the Act shall contain the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) avatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto number ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the number of the securities account opened and the date on which the securities account is opened; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise taotluse registripidajale edastanud kontohalduri &auml;rinimi; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the business name of the account administrator who forwarded the application for opening the securities account to the registrar; </inglise>
<eesti>3) juriidilisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku puhul registrikood, kui juriidiline isik on registreeritud; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the registry code of the owner of the securities account if the owner is a legal person and registered; </inglise>
<eesti>4) muud teatises sisalduva informatsiooni m&otilde;istmise seisukohalt registripidaja hinnangul t&auml;htsust omavad andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>4) other information which the registrar considers relevant for the comprehension of the information contained in the notice. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik ei ole teatise saamise &otilde;igusest loobunud, edastatakse see olenevalt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku poolt avaldatud ning registrisse kantud valikust kas posti teel v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava arvutiv&otilde;rgu kaudu elektroonsel kujul vastaval posti v&otilde;i elektronposti aadressil. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the owner of a securities account has not waived the right to receive a notice, it shall be sent to the owner by post or electronically through a public computer network to the corresponding postal or e-mail address according to the choice of the owner as entered in the Register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Ajutise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto korral edastatakse teatis v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kohta emitendile, kelle taotlusel ajutine v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avati, kui emitent pole sellest &otilde;igusest loobunud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the case of a temporary securities account, a notice concerning the opening of the securities account shall be sent to the issuer who requested the opening of the temporary securities account unless the issuer has waived such right. </inglise>
