<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te </eesti>
<inglise>Statement of securities account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Seaduse paragrahvi 20 l&otilde;ikes 5 nimetatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te peab sisaldama allj&auml;rgnevaid andmeid:: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A statement of a securities account as specified in subsection 20 (5) of the Act shall contain the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto number; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the number of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the name of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the address of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>4) vastavalt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku poolt teatatud ning registrisse kantud edastusre&zcaron;iimile k&otilde;ik registrisse kantud ning m&auml;&auml;ratud ajavahemiku sees v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol tehtud kanded, koos iga kande tegemise aja ja kande sisu selgitava m&auml;rkega; </eesti>
<inglise>4) according to the schedule and manner indicated by the owner of the securities account and entered in the register, all entries made in the securities account and entered in the register within a specified period of time together with the time of each entry and a description of the content of the entry; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte koostamise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the date of preparation of the statement; </inglise>
<eesti>6) periood (v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte periood), millises ajavahemikus tehtud kandeid koostatud v&auml;ljav&otilde;te kajastab; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the period (the period of the statement) during which the entries set out in the statement were made; </inglise>
<eesti>7) muud v&auml;ljav&otilde;ttes sisalduva informatsiooni m&otilde;istmise seisukohalt registripidaja hinnangul t&auml;htsust omavad andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>7) other information which the registrar considers relevant for the comprehension of the information contained in the statement. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te edastatakse olenevalt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku poolt avaldatud ning registrisse kantud valikust kas posti teel v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkasutatava arvutiv&otilde;rgu kaudu elektroonsel kujul vastaval posti v&otilde;i elektronposti aadressil. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A statement of a securities account shall be sent to the owner of the securities account by post or electronically through a public computer network to the corresponding postal or e-mail address according to the choice of the owner as entered in the Register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te edastatakse perioodiliselt vastavalt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku poolt teatatud ning registrisse kantud edastusre&zcaron;iimi valikust: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A statement of a securities account shall be sent to the owner of the securities account periodically according to the schedule and manner chosen by the owner and entered in the Register: </inglise>
<eesti>1) iga kalendrip&auml;eva kohta, kui selle sees tehti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole kanne; </eesti>
<inglise>1) concerning each calendar day if entries were made in the securities account during the corresponding day; </inglise>
<eesti>2) iga kalendaarse dekaadi kohta, kui selle sees tehti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole kanne; </eesti>
<inglise>2) concerning each ten calendar day period if entries were made in the securities account during the corresponding period; </inglise>
<eesti>3) iga kalendrikuu kohta, kui selle sees tehti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole kanne; </eesti>
<inglise>3) concerning each calendar month if entries were made in the securities account during the corresponding month; </inglise>
<eesti>4) iga kalendaarse kvartali kohta, kui selle sees tehti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole kanne v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>4) concerning each calendar quarter if entries were made in the securities account during the corresponding quarter, or </inglise>
<eesti>5) iga kalendriaasta kohta, kui selle sees tehti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>5) concerning each calendar year if entries were made in the securities account during the corresponding year. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ajutise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto korral edastatakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te emitendile, kelle taotlusel ajutine v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avati. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) In the case of a temporary securities account, a statement of the securities account shall be sent to issuer who requested the opening of the securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;te edastatakse emitendile vastavalt l&otilde;ike 3 punktis 5 s&auml;testatud edastusre&zcaron;iimile, kui emitent pole sellest &otilde;igusest loobunud. </eesti>
<inglise>The statement of the securities account shall be sent to the issuer according to the schedule and manner provided for in clause (3) 5) unless the issuer has waived such right. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus peatada v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;tete edastamine, kui on ilmnenud, et v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik v&otilde;i tema poolt nimetatud ja registrisse kantud isik pole saanud v&auml;ljav&otilde;tet l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud aadressi eba&otilde;igsuse t&otilde;ttu. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The registrar has the right to suspend the sending of statements of a securities account if it becomes evident that the owner of the securities account or the person indicated by the owner and entered in the Register has not received the statements due to the address specified in subsection (2) being incorrect. (1) RTL = Riigi Teataja Lisa = Appendix to the State Gazette </inglise>

